  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\"><img alt=\"House Drumm.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/50px-House_Drumm.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/75px-House_Drumm.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/100px-House_Drumm.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Dagon Drumm</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\"><img alt=\"House Drumm.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/50px-House_Drumm.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/75px-House_Drumm.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0f/House_Drumm.svg/100px-House_Drumm.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\">House Drumm</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dagon Drumm</b> is a legendary <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> raider of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\">House Drumm</a> who supposedly lived during the <a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a>. He is said to have been a <a href=\"/index.php/Necromancer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Necromancer\">necromancer</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dagon_Drumm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403155620\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.074 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.288 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 408/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10412/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4833/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 364/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 577/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 se